w tab-separated table with columns\n    `n_samples, n_sites, min_per_group, destrand, use_db, db_path` (`write_tsv`).\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- At least `output/unite_stats.tsv` must exist when you submit.\n- Full output set expected: unite_stats.tsv under `output/`.\n\nWhen the deliverables are in `output/`, call `submit_done(success=true)` with a short\nsummary of how you solved it.\n\n## Workspace (read-only summary)\n```json\n{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"mk_raw.rds\": {\n      \"_file\": \"mk_raw.rds\"\n    },\n    \"sampleA.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleA.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"sampleB.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleB.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"sampleC.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleC.bismark.cov\"\n    },\n    \"sampleD.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleD.bismark.cov\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/unite_stats.tsv` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_nZICcUQ9Fpsn4BjoUlq25LhG", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Load the methylKit library in R.\\n2. Use methylKit::methRead to read the four bismark-style coverage files with the specified parameters.\\n3. Run methylKit::unite on the loaded data.\\n4. Save the united methylBase object using saveRDS.\\n5. Create a single-row table with the specified columns and save it using write_tsv.\\n6. Verify the existence of output/unite_stats.tsv.\\n7. Submit the task as done if the file exists.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (418 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_nZICcUQ9Fpsn4BjoUlq25LhG"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_dDKEAiQ9XXqu0V3EJcXASd